- Create a new GitHub repository:

  https://github.com/new

  Repository name: byoc

  $ git remote add origin git@github.com:kalekundert/byoc.git
  $ git push -u origin master

- Create a "pending" trusted publisher:

  https://pypi.org/manage/account/publishing/

  PyPI project name: byoc
  Owner:             kalekundert
  Repository name:   byoc
  Workflow name:     release.yml

- Add Codecov token to GitHub:

  https://app.codecov.io/gh/kalekundert/byoc/new
  https://github.com/kalekundert/byoc/settings/secrets/actions/new

- Build the documentation:

  https://app.readthedocs.org/dashboard/import/
